com.ibm.es.ama.zing.common.model.axml

Interface CrawlData

  • All Superinterfaces:
    AXMLBase<CrawlData,Document>, java.lang.Cloneable, LazyAXML<CrawlData,Document>

    public interface CrawlData
extends LazyAXML<CrawlData,Document>
    Interface for accessing crawl-data component. Single crawl-url typically contains two crawl-data, one for metadata and the other for actual data, distinguished by their content-type. For accessing child document components from crawl-data object, use one of forEach, forEachBuild and map.
